item.title: Pizza is the best food ever and here is why. Can you tell I like it?
item.description: Yahoo! JAPAN is one of the largest media companies in Japan, providing services such as search, news, e-commerce, and e-mail. Over 50 million users log in to Yahoo! JAPAN services every month. Over the years, there were many attacks on user accounts and issues that led to lost account access. Most of these issues were related to password usage for authentication. With recent advances in authentication technology, Yahoo! JAPAN has decided to move from password-based to passwordless authentication.
